(20, 'SIMPLE', '<h2>Money Training Center will provide a simple, easy to understand and common sense roadmap to help you meet your goal to STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK.</h2><h2>As you travel on your road to STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK, you will reach many important milestones. Learn to appreciate reaching each of these milestone.</h2><h2>You are not expected to follow your roadmap perfectly, but the closer you follow your roadmap, the faster you will reach your final destination - STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK.<br></h2><h1><font color=\"#0b0499\"></font></h1>', '$meta_title mai', '$meta_keywords', '$meta_description', 1),
(21, 'EASY TO UNDERSTAND', '<h2>\r\n\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 18.15pt;\">Money Training Center will take a small step by small step approach to makes it easy for everyone to understand what to do to stop LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK. </h2><h2>Each small step will be a building block for the next small step.</h2><pre><h2><br></h2></pre>', 'EASY TO UNDERSTAND', 'EASY TO UNDERSTAND', 'Money Training Center long term Mission: Stop Working Americans from LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK.\r\n', 1),
(22, 'MOSTLY COMMOM SENSE', '<h2>Many Working Americans have been brainwashed to think it requires a lot of education and it requires a lot of time to&nbsp; STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK. This is not true.</h2><h2>To stop LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK requires mostly common sense and approximately one hour a week to follow Money Training Center roadmap … about the amount of time it takes to watch a housewife reality TV show or any other hour long TV Show.</h2>', 'MOSTLY COMMOM SENSE', 'MOSTLY COMMOM SENSE', 'MOSTLY COMMOM SENSE', 1),
(23, 'RULES OF GOLD', '<font style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 49, 99);\"></font><h2>Rules of Gold are powerful, though provoking ideas, yet easy to understand because they are written using simple words you use every day. </h2><h2>These Rules of Gold are \"more valuable than money in the bank.\" They are like training wheels on a bike; they keep you from hurting yourself while you are learning to ride the bike or in this case, keep you from hurting yourself while you are learning to STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK.&nbsp;</h2>', 'RULES OF GOLD n', 'RULES OF GOLD n', 'RULES OF GOLD n', 1);
