(1, 1, 0, 'Module # 001', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><br></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; text-align: center; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>WELCOME\r\nTO MONEY TRAINING CENTER</span></b></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><a name=\"_Hlk534749620\"><span style=\'background: lime; margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'><font color=\"#000000\">(Module\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span># 1)</font></span></a></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>ORIENTATION</span></b></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Hello and welcome to Money\r\nTraining Center. You are the newest member to join the Money Training Center\r\n(MTC) Team.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Money Training Center <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">was founded</span> because of the Great Recession of\r\n2008.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Money\r\nTraining Center Founding Principle:</span></b><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> </span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>“<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">Working\r\nAmericans” </i>have been brainwashed to make money decisions that are in the\r\nbest interest of “Other People” and not in their own best interest.<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"> <i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">THIS</span> BRAINWASHING MUST STOP!!!</i></b><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><sup> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></sup></i></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(128, 96, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>[ROG # 1]<span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> &nbsp;</span></span></i></b></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px; line-height: 150%;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(128, 96, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></i></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Money Training Center\r\nMission:</span></b><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"background: white; margin: 0px;\">Provide<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span>a simple, easy to understand and common sense\r\nroadmap to help<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"> “Working Americans”</i> </span></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>.&nbsp;</span></b></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>This first week will <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">be completed</span> in two parts. The first part will be\r\na very brief orientation about <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">Money</span>\r\nTraining Center. The second part will start you on your road <a name=\"_Hlk524408806\"></a><a name=\"_Hlk518206329\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><font color=\"#1f3864\">trip to </font></span></a></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>STOP</span></i></b></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(47, 84, 150); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>.</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'><font color=\"#000000\"> </font></span></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><a name=\"_Hlk517163512\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">A)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>At </span></a><a name=\"_Hlk534461645\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>the\r\nstart of each week, some commonly used words will be defined to make sure<span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> you and your MTC Team are on the same page.</span> A\r\nbrief <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">discussion</span> of each <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">commonly</span> used word will also <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">be included</span>. The <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">commonly</span> use words that will <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">be defined</span>\r\nthis week </span></span></a></span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>are:</span></span></span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">1)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></i><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>LIVING PAYCHECK TO\r\nPAYCHECK </span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>- </span></i></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>If you do not have\r\nenough money today to pay all the bills you will have over the next six months.</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Brief Discussion:&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 96px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">a)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>People will often say they are </span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:&#10;normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>LIVING PAYCHECK TO\r\nPAYCHECK</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>, </span></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>but most of the time they\r\ncannot define what </span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>LIVING PAYCHECK TO\r\nPAYCHECK</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">really</span> means. They do not have a <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">well-defined</span> target. Without a clear <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">understanding of what your target is,</span> it will difficult\r\nfor you to know if you are moving closer to or farther away from your <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">target.</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 96px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">b)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Think of a person playing basketball in a dark gym at night. This person\r\nwould miss his/her target most of the time if he/she <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">were</span> shooting a basketball in a dark gym at night.&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 96px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">c)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>If you do not have a clear understanding of what </span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">really</span> means, you\r\nwill miss your target because you will be “shooting in the dark<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">.”</span>&nbsp;</span></span><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">2)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Money\r\n– </span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>It’s\r\nusually a piece of paper or a piece of metal that has been given a number\r\nvalue.</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> It is <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">a</span> non-living <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">thing\r\nwithout feelings or emotions.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Brief discussion:</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 96px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">a)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Everyone uses <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">money</span>, but if asked\r\nwhat <span sty