(259, 2, 0, 'Module # 024', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'background: lime; margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'>(Section # 24)</span></i></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">A)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Question #2: Why <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">should you reduce or eliminate </span>emotions money decisions?\r\n</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">1)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>ANSWER: Since Money<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"> </i>is only numbers\r\nyou add, subtract, multiply or divide. Adding, subtracting, multiplying or\r\ndividing numbers is done more <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">effectively</span>\r\nif you think with <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">your</span> head and follow\r\nthe emotions of your heart.<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></b></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">2)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Brief discussion</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 120px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">a)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span>Money is most often represented in\r\nthe U. S. by a piece of paper called: 1 dollar bill; 5 dollar bill; 10 dollar\r\nbill; 20 dollar bill; 50 dollar bill and 100 dollar bill.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 120px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">b)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>The total</span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> amount of all your bills need to be less than the total\r\namount of your paycheck. </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 120px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">c)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>The more you increase the <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">total amount</span>\r\nof your paychecks and decrease the <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">total amount</span>\r\nof your bills, the more things you can buy for you and your family. </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 168px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">Ø<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(255, 192, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Once <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">y<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">ou start to think of money as nothing but a number,\r\nthen it will be easier to stop making emotional money decisions.<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></b></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><sup><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>[ROG\r\n# 9]</span></sup></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 168px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">Ø<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>\r\n</span></span></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(255, 192, 0); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>You will make wiser\r\nmoney decisions if you use your head and not your heart.<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span></span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><sup><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>[ROG # 10]</span></sup></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></b><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 168px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">Ø<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margi