mal;\'>\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>You <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">will</span> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">miss</span> your target to</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> STOP</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> </span></i></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> if you are shooting in the dark because you <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">don’t know</span> where your money goes</span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 120px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">c)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>According to <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">a Gallup poll taken in June\r\nof<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span>2013</span>, almost 7 out of 10\r\nAmericans do not know where their money goes (no budget).</span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 168px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">Ø<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>\r\n</span></span></span></span><a href=\"https://www.deseretnews.com/article/865581100/New-Gallup-poll-shows-two-thirds-of-Americans-do-not-budget.html\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><u><font color=\"#0563c1\" face=\"Calibri\" size=\"3\">https://www.deseretnews.com/article/865581100/New-Gallup-poll-shows-two-thirds-of-Americans-do-not-budget.html</font></u></span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 150%;\"></span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 120px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">d)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>The most <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">powerful</span> weapon “<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">Other People”</i> use against you is the\r\n“KEEP YOU IGNORANT”<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span>weapon.<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span><a name=\"_Hlk526140610\"></a></span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"margin: 0px;\"></span>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 150px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span