(269, 2, 0, 'Module # 034', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'background: lime; margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;</span>(Section\r\n# 34)</span><span style=\'margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px; line-height: 150%;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>A FEW KEY POINTS FROM THIS WEEK</span></b><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>In 15 words or less, insert what you think about\r\neach of the Key Points listed below:</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">A)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>According to national news and polling organization, up to 75% of “Working\r\nAmericans” <i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">are<b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"> </b></i></span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK</span></i></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>.<span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </span> </span></b><span style=\'margin: 0px; padding: 0in; border: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>&lt;Data Box</span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </span> </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">B)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>You are </span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:&#10;normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>LIVING PAYCHECK TO\r\nPAYCHECK</span></i></b><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'> </span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>because “<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">Other People”</i> are waging an aggressive\r\nand on-going fight to make you spend your money in the best interest of “<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">Other People”</i> and not in your own best\r\ninterest.<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0in; border: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: none;\">&lt;Data Box</span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </span> </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">C)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Making </span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>money\r\ndecisions </span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>that\r\nare in your best interest </span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>is not about being well educated or knowing some trick. It’s about getting\r\n</span><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>useful\r\ninformation about money, getting <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">useful</span>\r\nanswers to <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">important</span> money questions, <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">gaining</span> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">useful</span>\r\n<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">money skills</i>, <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">and</span> <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">using good</span> <i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">money tools</i></span><i><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>.<span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp; </span></span></i><span style=\'margin: 0px; padding: 0in; border: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: none; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>&lt;Data Box</span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">D)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>The most <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">powerful</span> weapon “<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">Other People”</i> use to make you spend <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">your</span> money in their interest is to keep you\r\nignorant. <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0in; border: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: none;\">&lt;Data Box</span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"> </span> </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>&nbsp;</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10.66px 72px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">E)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>Knowing where your money goes is the first step you need to take to stop\r\nspending <span style=\"margin: 0px;\">your</span> money in the best interest\r\nof <i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">“Other People.”</i> <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0in; border: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: none;\">&lt;Data Box</span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<b></b><i></i><u></u><sub></sub><sup></sup><strike></strike><font size=\"3\"></font><font face=\"Times New Roman\"></font><br></p>', NULL, NULL, 1, '2018-12-27 02:54:23');
