(270, 2, 0, 'Module # 035', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\'background: lime; margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'>(Section # 35)</span><span style=\'margin: 0px; line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 13.33px; line-height: 150%;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>END OF WEEK # 2 </span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;\'></span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 48px; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><a name=\"_Hlk517112409\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'><span style=\"margin: 0px;\">A)<span style=\'font: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"; margin: 0px; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\'>&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\'background: white; margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>During the very first week, you were told if you want to </span></a><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(83, 129, 53); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>STOP LIVING PAYCHECK TO PAYCHECK</span></i></b></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;\"><span style=\'margin: 0px; color: rgb(31, 56, 100); line-height: 150%; font-family: \"Arial\",sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\'>, <span style=\"background: white; margin: 0px;\">you must meet five\r\nrequirements. These five requirements will